# Ripgrep extra ignores for AeroVista workspaces.
# Used by X:\.CODEX\tools\safe-rg.ps1.
#
# Notes:
# - These are "safe defaults" to avoid accidental scans of huge, usually-unhelpful folders.
# - Override by running rg directly, or update this file when you intentionally want to include a folder.

# VCS / tooling
.git/
.hg/
.svn/

# Common build / dependency outputs
node_modules/
dist/
build/
out/
.next/
.nuxt/
.svelte-kit/
.parcel-cache/
.turbo/
.cache/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.venv/
venv/
__pycache__/

# OS / Windows junk
System Volume Information/
$RECYCLE.BIN/
FOUND.000/

# Common large artifacts
*.iso
*.img
*.vhd
*.vhdx
*.qcow2
*.qcow2.*
*.dmg
*.exe

# This workspace (X:\) top-level folders that are often massive and rarely search targets.
# Comment out items here when you intentionally need to search inside them.
Backup/
core-backup-*/
libvirt-images/
vaults/

